metadata.name: Blur Go Burr 1
metadata.description:

**__EVERY 1000 MINTS WE INCREASE IT BY 1.5%!__**

*GRAB YOUR BLUR BURR TICKETS NOW. WE ALL MOON TOGETHER.*
